<subSubSection id="F4317990C854F3930B8B01C9AB277507" pageId="0" pageNumber="79" type="habit and habitat">
<paragraph id="301FF42DDB75DA6B132314C2C25F0286" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">Habit and habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="ADAF29133276F7985FDADA1C092B2404" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">Scattered to gregarious on the ground covered with dead and decaying conifer needles, from summer to autumn.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
